<mjml>
  <mj-head>
    <mj-font name="Open Sans" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css?family=Open+Sans" />
  </mj-head>
  <mj-body>
    <mj-container>
      <mj-section>
        <mj-column>
          <mj-text font-family="Open Sans, helvetica" font-size="30" color="#505050" align="center">Daily Downbeat</mj-text>
        </mj-column>
      </mj-section>
      <mj-section background-color="#0275d8">
        <mj-column>
          <mj-text font-size="20px" color="#FFF" font-family="Open Sans, helvetica" align="center">Welcome, <%= @user.username %> !</mj-text>
        </mj-column>
      </mj-section>
      <mj-section background-color="#F0F0F0">
        <mj-column>
          <mj-text font-size="16px" color="#505050" font-family="Open Sans, helvetica">Hello,</mj-text>
          <mj-text font-size="16px" color="#505050" font-family="Open Sans, helvetica">I just wanted to thank you for creating an account on Daily Downbeat. Whether making posts, adding valuable comments, or voting on user content, account holders like yourself are responsible for making Daily Downbeat the online music community that it is.</mj-text>
          <mj-text font-size="16px" color="#505050" font-family="Open Sans, helvetica">Daily Downbeat is still very young. It took plenty of hard work getting the website to it's current state, but I already know there's plenty more to do. While you're becoming acquainted with the Daily Downbeat community, feel free to send me any comments, questions, or suggestions about the website.</mj-text>
          <mj-text font-size="16px" color="#505050" font-family="Open Sans, helvetica">In the meantime, feel free to <a href="http://www.dailydownbeat.com/" target="_blank">peruse</a>.</mj-text>
          <mj-text font-size="16px" color="#505050" font-family="Open Sans, helvetica">Again, thank you,</mj-text>
          <mj-text font-size="16px" color="#505050" font-family="Open Sans, helvetica" line-height="6px">Louis Cruz</mj-text>
          <mj-text font-size="14px" color="#808080" font-family="Open Sans, helvetica" line-height="6px">Creator of Daily Downbeat</mj-text>
          <mj-divider border-color="#505050"></mj-divider>
          <mj-text font-size="12px" color="#505050" font-family="Open Sans, helvetica">If you did not initiate the creation of a Daily Downbeat account for <%= @user.email %>, please <a href="http://www.dailydownbeat.com/#/contact" target="_blank">contact us</a> as soon as possible.</mj-text>
        </mj-column>
      </mj-section>
    </mj-container>
  </mj-body>
</mjml>
